   transportation   the island is served by pantelleria airport,http://www.pantelleriairport.it/home/default.aspx which is served by alitalia throughout the year , connecting trapani and palermo , and various other companies in summer , connecting the island with main italian cities such as milan , rome , venice , and others .

world geography : this large island forms an autonomous region of italy along with smaller islands , like pantelleria

